        Toggle AI          /
     
     Spaceship Power
        Focus Group 1      1
        Focus Group 2      2
        Focus Group 3      3
        
     Spaceship HUD
        HUD Cyc Foreward   '
        HUD Cyc Back       ;
        HUD Tab1-10        F1-F10
        HUD Open ScoreB    tab
        HUD Toggle Max     F11
        HUD Interact       home
        HUD Confirm        enter
        HUD cancel         rctrl
        HUD left pane up   up
        HUD left pane down down
        HUD left pane left left
        HUD left pane right right
        Comm Open Chat     \
        Come Show Chat     =
        Comm Open Precan   lctrl+\
        
     IFCS Controls
        IFCS A             rctrl+a
        IFCS B             rctrl+b
        IFCS X             rctrl+x
        IFCS Y             rctrl+y
    
